cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.IR 

This paper involves computer vision and deep learning techniques to detect crop damage from aerial imagery. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning algorithms, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of unmanned aerial systems (UAS) suggests that it could belong to cs.RO (Robotics). Finally, the paper involves the analysis of large datasets, which suggests that it could belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
